<P>&startq;Why&mdash;it was all over ink, and good for nothing,
&s;o I did not think of your mi&s;&s;ing it&mdash;&s;o I throwed
it behind the fire.&endq;</P>
<P>&startq;I wi&s;h you had been thrown there your&s;elf with
all my heart! But if ever you bring a broom into
